Title: REST API: fixing folder show endpoints when folder has network scan option configured
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: core
Date: 1630492987
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0p10

In the previous version, the REST API returned a 500 error when the user attempted
to query a folder which has the network scan attribute configured. This werk fixes
this behaviour and correctly displays any time related entries.
